column15:
Schedule Set
This particular property I can is one of the most difficult to reach, because (1) The PIC (apparently the son of the owner of the hotel) was never answered my calls, and (2) I was given the owner (the father of the PIC) number, and I sent him SMS and also several calls, but the same, he never answered at all, and (3) tho I sent 3 follow up emails to the hotel, the staff reluctantly to reply and to secure any schedule with us ; they asked me to call the PIC / owner first (but then again, the PIC was never answered) ; it was just a hellish loop of the same thing.

But luckily, we finally secure the schedule by today. The reservation staff named Ms. Heny was taking the responsibility to secure the schedule and help us to have the photo shoot by today.

REQUEST FROM THE HOTEL 

Also, there is 1 request from Ms. Heny :

Traveloka listed STANDARD ROOM WITH FAN on their website and informing that the room also have a TV. But, the room actually do not have TV. So there are guests who book the room from Traveloka, and when they arrive knowing there is no TV on the Standard Fan Room, they complain to the hotel. (And this happen more than once).

So she asked me kindly if I can tell Traveloka to update the info the the standard room with fan (that the room is not equipped with TV).

Responding Ariana’s comment : roger that, and your welcome. | 27 July 2016

Note : This is the most huge property I’ve ever shot ever. Spent a total of 7 hours (+ 1 hour of break) to cover all the facilities and rooms. By far, the property is the biggest and have numbers of facilities. They have 1 cafe, 2 lounges,  2 restos, complete spa & fitness facilities (gym + separated sauna for female & male, relax rooms for male & female, hot water bath for female & male). 

They have 6 type of rooms, which 3 of them are Suites type - Club Suite, Executive Suite, and Presidential Suite -
(that need shot treatment just like 1 property for each rooms since the suite type rooms have living room, kitchen, guest bathroom, etc) ; 2 regular rooms type which are Premium Room and Tower Room ;

and 1 Penthouse (that is exclusively take 1 whole floor) that have 2 additional guest rooms complete with bathrooms for each rooms, garden, dining room, living room, etc.

So please kindly anticipate for huge number of pics delivery. | 26 July 2016 - (I create folder for each rooms / facilities)
